folder_text = "[b][color=#093C5D]Algorithm[/color][/b]
An [color=#3B7597]algorithm[/color] is a step-by-step procedure used to solve a problem.

Example:
Start
Input two numbers
Add the numbers
Display the result
End

[b][color=#093C5D]Pseudocode[/color][/b]
[color=#3B7597]Pseudocode [/color]is a simple way of writing program logic using plain English-like statements.

Purpose:
[color=#3B7597]Plan[/color] the program before coding
[color=#3B7597]Understand[/color] logic easily
[color=#3B7597]Detect[/color] logical errors early

Example:
START
INPUT number
IF number > 0
DISPLAY \"Positive\"
ELSE
DISPLAY \"Negative\"
END
"

