experiment_text = "[b][color=#093C5D]Loops[/color][/b]
[color=#3B7597]Loops [/color]repeat code multiple times.

[b][color=#093C5D]for Loop[/color][/b]
Used when the number of [color=#3B7597]repetitions[/color] is known.

Example:
for(int i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {
   [color=#831C91]System.out.println(i);[/color]
}

[b][color=#093C5D]while Loop[/color][/b]
Repeats while a [color=#3B7597]condition[/color] is true.

Example:
while(number > 0) {
   number--;
}

"

